<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PlayUs</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style/font.css">
    <style type="text/css">

        body {
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(100deg, rgba(159, 148, 250, 1) 0%, rgba(88, 92, 255, 1) 100%);
        }

        .container {
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-flow: row nowrap;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .sub-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-flow: column nowrap;
            margin-left: 10rem;
            color:white;
        }

        .btn-start {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: #5f62e2;
            width: 400px;
            padding-top: 1vw;
            padding-bottom: 1vw;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-style: none;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 6px 1px #53519a;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: none;
        }

        .image-container {
            width: 730px;
        }

        .main-images {
            height: auto;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="container">
        <section class="sub-container">
            <span class="h1-like kanit semiBold">Play Us</span>
            <p class="h3-like spoqaHanSans regular">웹서버 구현을 공부하지 않고<br>데이터 조작 & 리턴 가능한 서비스</p>
            <br>
            <input type="button" class="btn-start spoqaHanSans bold" value="시작하기" onclick="btn_start_click()">
        </section>
        <section class="image-container">
            <img class="main-images" src="images/main.png" alt="PlayUs">
        </section>
    </main>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        var isLogin = <%= isLogin %>;
        var hasProject = <%= hasProject %>;
        function btn_start_click() {
            location.href = isLogin ? hasProject ? "/projectList" : "/createProject" :  "/login";
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>